c=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9d%2FTheHustle2019.jpg&h=813ab942&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.阿拉丁，一個和猴子阿布在阿拉伯城市阿格拉巴的善良的年輕人，在一次際遇中拯救茉莉公主並與她成為朋友；茉莉厭倦了處處受到庇護的生活於是偷偷逃出宮外探索，與此同時，大臣賈方計劃推翻茉莉的父親成為蘇丹。他和他的寵物鸚鵡艾格尋找隱藏在奇蹟之穴中的魔燈，想藉由神燈實現願望。而奇跡之穴只有一個稱為「未經琢磨的鑽石」的人能進入，於是他找上阿拉丁，說服阿拉丁為他進洞穴拿取神燈。在洞穴內，阿拉丁還發現了魔毯、也找到了神燈，但因為阿布撿起紅寶石洞穴開始坍塌。阿拉丁拼死一搏把燈交給賈方後居然被賈方踢進洞穴，辛虧阿布即時把神燈從賈方身上偷了回來<br />\n<br />\n2.安妮&middot;海瑟薇將加盟蕾蓓爾&middot;威爾森新片《壞壞女郎》(Nasty Women，暫譯)。影片翻拍自1988年弗蘭克&middot;奧茲執導，史蒂夫&middot;馬丁、邁克爾&middot;凱恩主演的《騙徒臭事多》。片中安妮&middot;海瑟薇、蕾蓓爾&middot;威爾森化身女版騙徒，當然此次她們的目標將是鮮嫩多汁的&ldquo;單身男子&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n11 00PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=8dca8420\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=12Rr7FHSceVDny91Y6RlLIaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=3bf3fe9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b220b48c4ebc04e57039755bf2623d2055b05cad","tid":1429763,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de2a80b929d3c68365a13cb6fd50904278011050","tid":1429763,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi